---
---

<section id="achievements" class="bg-dark px-4 py-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-white">
      核心<span class="text-gold">成果</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gold mx-auto mb-16"></div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- AI 研究成果卡片 -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-lg border-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-all p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark/80">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">AI 研究成果</h3>
              <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-gold"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
              <img src="/gongzhonghao.jpg" alt="公众号二维码" class="w-16 h-16 rounded align-middle shadow-lg" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            公众号「谢先生的AI深析札记」已发布文章，涵盖产业分析、Agent 架构、本地部署实战。
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold">→</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">中国 AI 产业格局</span>一超多强、四龙夺珠</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold">→</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">Agent 思考模式</span>智能体决策链设计</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gold/20">
            <a href="/research" class="text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors font-semibold">
              进入研究库 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 督友小程序卡片 -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-lg border-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-all p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark/80">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">督友小程序</h3>
              <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-gold"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
              <img src="/duyou.jpeg" alt="督友小程序码" class="w-16 h-16 rounded align-middle shadow-lg" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            强迫症式轻社群自律监督应用。采用混合云架构，支持离线网络缓存自动降级，打造无缝体验。
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold">→</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">架构设计</span>API 优先 + 本地回退</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold">→</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">离线支撑</span>断网环境无缝打卡</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gold/20">
            <a href="/duyou" class="text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors font-semibold">
              查看详情 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 企业 AI 技能递送方案卡片 -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-lg border-2 border-gold/50 hover:border-gold transition-all p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark/80 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(212,175,55,0.05)]">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">企业 AI 技能递送</h3>
              <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-gold"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gold opacity-50">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 font-medium">
            与其支付高昂的人力完成繁琐录入，不如交付一套“听话、高效、不出错”的自动化流程。让 AI 真正接管您的老旧系统与专业软件。
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold font-bold">●</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">降本增效</span> 比雇佣初级文员更划算</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold font-bold">●</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">落地闭环</span> 交付不休息的自动化生产力</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold font-bold">●</span>
              <span><span class="text-white font-semibold">安全合规</span> 数据不出内网，账号原生安全</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gold/20">
            <a href="/delivery" class="text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
              查看详情 & 深度演示 <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 支付与财务 AI 深度研究卡片 -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-lg border-2 border-gold/30 hover:border-gold transition-all p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark/80 opacity-60">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
 
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">支付与财务 AI 深度研究</h3>
          <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-gold mb-6"></div>
 
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
            深耕支付行业 20 年。专注于支付风控、金融科技合规以及企业财务 AI 化转型的深度融合探索。
          </p>
 
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gold">●</span>
              <span>研究预研中 · 2026 Q3 发布</span>
            </div>
          </div>
 
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gold/20">
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">敬请期待</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>